msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:314
msgid ""
"Hold `Ctrl` then select the cells of the row or column dimension values that "
"should be grouped."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:315
msgid ""
"Right-click one of the selected cells, then click :icon:`fa-plus-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Group pivot dimensions`. A new dimension is added to "
